snippet.title: vivid/stasis - V2.0.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2093940

Hajimeli and SKY HOUR WORKS are bringing the freeware, non-commercial rhythm game "vivid/stasis" to Steam in Q1 2023, launching with the first chapter of its episodic storyline!
